      {
        "Language": "POL",
        "Name": "\u015Awie\u0107 silniej ni\u017C s\u0142o\u0144ce",
        "Client": "Pustynny Starszy",
        "Description": "Gor\u0105cy wiatr wieje z R\u00F3wnin\r\nPiasku. Ten sam wiatr czu\u0142em,\r\ngdy Teostra obr\u00F3ci\u0142 ca\u0142\u0105\r\nwiosk\u0119 w popi\u00F3\u0142. Prosz\u0119,\r\nzatrzymaj t\u0119 straszn\u0105 besti\u0119!",
        "Target": "Zabij Teostr\u0119",
        "Fail": "Nagroda r\u00F3wna 0 lub\r\nkoniec czasu"
      },
      {
        "Language": "POR",
        "Name": "Mais Brilhante que o Sol",
        "Client": "Anci\u00E3o do Deserto",
        "Description": "Um vento calcinante sopra da\r\nPlan\u00EDcie Arenosa. O mesmo que\r\nsenti vindo de um Teostra que\r\ntornou a aldeia num mar de\r\nchamas. Eu imploro, detenha\r\naquela fera maldita!",
        "Target": "Mate um Teostra",
        "Fail": "A recompensa chega a 0\r\nou o tempo expira"
      },
      {
        "Language": "KOR",
        "Name": "\uD0C0\uC624\uB974\uB294 \uD0DC\uC591\uBCF4\uB2E4 \uBD89\uAC8C",
